apiVersion: 
 - Refering to this cheatsheet: 
 - https://matthewpalmer.net/kubernetes-app-developer/articles/kubernetes-apiversion-definition-guide.html
 
kind:
 - what type of entity is built eg. deployment or service
 
metadata:
 - name
 - label
   - app
   
spec:
 - replicas -> how many should be present of the configurated entity?
 - selector
   - matchLabels -> which label needs to match in order for it to be recognized as matching entity?


   

  
